ActPilotage Act
PrecisReappointment of LAURIA ANNE GALBRAITH of Halifax, Nova Scotia, as part-time Chairperson of the Atlantic Pilotage Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year or until such time as a new Chairperson is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective February 5, 2018.
